Package: bestsubset
Title: Best Subset Selection via MIQP using Gurobi
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Edoardo", "Lanzettu", , "edoardo.lanzetti@epfl.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements an exact algorithm for Best Subset Selection in linear 
    regression using Mixed-Integer Quadratic Programming (MIQP). By leveraging 
    the 'Gurobi' optimizer and Big-M constraints, it finds the globally optimal 
    subset of predictors of size k, minimizing the Residual Sum of Squares (RSS).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
